@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kpmoel(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v2 + 0.75 - tmp + 0.88)))
    v0 = wp.sin(((v1 + 0.02 / tmp + 0.95) + (tmp + 0.70 / v2 + 0.21)))
    data[tid] = v0
